propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>Promise.reject()</strong></code> 方法返回一个带有拒绝原因的 <code>Promise</code> 对象。</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/promise-reject.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>Promise.reject(reason)</var>;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"reason\">reason</dt>\n <dd>表示<code>Promise</code>被拒绝的原因。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>一个给定原因了的被拒绝的&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>静态函数 <code>Promise.reject</code> 返回一个被拒绝的 <code>Promise</code> 对象。通过使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Error\"><code>Error</code></a> 的实例获取错误原因 <code>reason</code> 对调试和选择性错误捕捉很有帮助。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用静态_promise.reject_方法","title":"使用静态 <code>Promise.reject()</code> 方法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>Promise.reject(new Error('fail')).then(function() {\n  // not called\n}, function(error) {\n  console.error(error); // Stacktrace\n});</code></pre>","titleAsText":"使用静态 Promise.reject() 方法"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">备注</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-promise.reject\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Promise.reject</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>ECMA 规范的首次定义</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-promise.reject\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Promise.reject</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Promise.reject","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise/reject/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"描述","id":"description"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Promise.reject() 方法返回一个带有拒绝原因的 Promise 对象。","popularity":0.0018,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Promise.reject()","lo